{"title":"MUE_Sepsis_Shock_Septico","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/MUE - Medicina de Urgencia/MUE_Sepsis_Shock_Septico.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"SEPSIS Y SHOCK SÉPTICO EN URGENCIAS","guid":"HE8yNF87RgadX1vOzP32HQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"DEFINICIONES Y CRITERIOS (Sepsis-3, 2016)","guid":"cfHDtICuTgSRSLAxWNq0ZA","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Sepsis","guid":"nTWJM_wqQkKWjzIqZSh-Vg","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"→ Disfunción orgánica vital x respuesta desregulada del huésped a infección","guid":"6g5msJA2SnKo_ui1g7tN3Q","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"→ SOFA ≥2 puntos sobre basal","guid":"yi-E0N37Td-X4Z7h26sqqw","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"→ Mortalidad hospitalaria ≥10%","guid":"lUe04AOhQaWk2hRzS6VioQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Shock séptico","guid":"UM00hhZLSOuczpk3FX9QSQ","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"→ Sepsis + necesidad de vasopresores para PAM ≥65 mmHg","guid":"POGiKMBrRN-sL11Zgv3tcQ","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"→ + Lactato >2 mmol/L tras reanimación adecuada","guid":"DWD2rj_zSS2Xc75KMMcg6w","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"6","text":"→ Mortalidad hospitalaria >40%","guid":"MpGl30fLT4iQ5kHFi5FDug","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"qSOFA (SCREENING EN URGENCIAS)","guid":"vhEC1BZYSVyEFeZp59ZhdQ","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"→ PAS ≤100 mmHg","guid":"MuM4ybKOQOaAHHQf1RcGmQ","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"→ FR ≥22/min","guid":"8npAizN_QFu0Ry4r2KyRRQ","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"→ Glasgow ≤13","guid":"Ae1H2eFVQU-JzHCFbxKQ0A","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"10","text":"→ ≥2 criterios → sospechar sepsis → evaluar SOFA","guid":"Z2s7muXFTISPmpV79ymtnA","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"10","text":"LIMITACIÓN: Sensibilidad baja (54%) → NO usar como criterio único","guid":"jR0CaDgwT4yej3VIQSGUEQ","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"10","text":"EN ADULTO MAYOR: Rendimiento aún menor x alteración basal de conciencia y PA","guid":"3Y3VDhqXTASVOzjIk0MyGA","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"1","text":"SOFA (DIAGNÓSTICO)","guid":"Uf805OsBTj-gQZtyS75SWQ","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"→ PaO2/FiO2 (respiratorio)","guid":"yHObfySWTcmhb4Jgswr8mQ","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"→ Plaquetas (coagulación)","guid":"WD5qsdS_QKmOiE7t7amYrw","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"→ Bilirrubina (hepático)","guid":"6cUsFRI7QeGTAECPh81lSw","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"17","text":"→ PAM y DVA (cardiovascular)","guid":"W04eBCOeRvuvcuXLfmRIoA","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"17","text":"→ Glasgow (neurológico)","guid":"QQ_SYsT_SkKtbDq99kPNOw","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"17","text":"→ Creatinina/diuresis (renal)","guid":"SQm_NJU0QT6z_4KVsNitwg","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"17","text":"PERLA: Cambio SOFA ≥2 sobre BASAL del paciente, NO sobre 0","guid":"RxIwINO8TZ2IjEdT-kRDSQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"1","text":"NEWS ≥5 como alternativa de screening","guid":"zf6Vkvr4RA6e-Qx_VZlK-w","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"→ Mejor sensibilidad que qSOFA en adultos mayores","guid":"Nay5wbpKQA6pq0rqjQNWag","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"→ Validado en urgencias (Churpek 2017)","guid":"gihKnhP7R9eKeqzVdOdLBw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"0","text":"EPIDEMIOLOGÍA","guid":"tttidao7TEazUkZwujjdWQ","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"Incidencia global → 48.9M casos/año","guid":"HRz1g5FyR6SwvlEFYlF6AQ","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"Mortalidad global → 11M muertes/año","guid":"7JdL0qATSJ2OrtvScE4hZw","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"EEUU → >1/3 muertes hospitalarias = sepsis","guid":"AmEopG40QnCd1Jj6ZQHGaA","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"28","text":"Focos más frecuentes","guid":"lxTOPFbbSBmHQWLFq7n8Vg","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"→ Pulmonar: 40-60%","guid":"wfoQWFo-QsORrm6pgtqPCQ","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"→ Urinario: 15-30%","guid":"EwEgqsf3QCma8GPjKQrDzg","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"→ Abdominal: 15-30%","guid":"aqOW9-UnSFOBi3ei00FSMA","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"32","text":"→ Piel/partes blandas: 5-10%","guid":"gtwfktSVTWu2Vpv5h2yfKA","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"32","text":"→ Sin foco identificado: 10-20%","guid":"Uk-OzrEAQCC-3XmWCH4XWQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"28","text":"EN ADULTO MAYOR","guid":"SdsetRYVQhOpoT4JcX3bWw","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"→ Incidencia 3-5x mayor que adultos jóvenes","guid":"EB0WuFhZT8aRsDZA5ViEtw","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"38","text":"→ Mortalidad 50-60% en >80 años con shock séptico","guid":"8PjT9eJzRSe5-viK0Mlg8Q","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"38","text":"→ Foco urinario relativamente más frecuente","guid":"ztol9wq4QG-eczLhzVzXzw","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"38","text":"→ Bacteriemia sin foco identificable más común","guid":"KMhRaWGVRyWstaf_hlgvaw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"0","text":"FISIOPATOLOGÍA","guid":"Npopfu7yQ1q5n0rsy4D1xg","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"Respuesta inmune desregulada","guid":"Yq3s7tfIT8mNrtp5_29ydg","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"→ Activación masiva citoquinas (IL-1, IL-6, TNF-α)","guid":"yEw0iDrzQ1KMXH6EH9aWEg","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"→ Activación complemento y coagulación","guid":"Zb1byZMXTTS3F_H-voy2Uw","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"44","text":"→ Daño endotelial difuso","guid":"-FVaQiOdTvm6fK0iVTAiqg","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"44","text":"→ Fuga capilar → edema tisular","guid":"ztiYSFE3RtubLx8EQgLT-w","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"43","text":"Disfunción microcirculatoria","guid":"ntJwNXpFSPCDY2cYnzgDFA","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"→ Microtrombos","guid":"V3-OZlPaQsKlqZaCghuDDw","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"→ Alteración flujo capilar","guid":"Ij_b_A29QfqmvO7mXj2xiA","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"49","text":"→ Maldistribución del flujo","guid":"0ntK1QrYTHKmXRlTqAqtSA","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"49","text":"→ Hipoxia celular a pesar de macrohemodinámica corregida","guid":"6KbMmUD6QPOVIR1RBTrUHw","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"43","text":"Disfunción mitocondrial","guid":"88bGBGyDT0qzoxA76m4bww","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"→ Incapacidad utilización O2","guid":"Bng94yWtTsuNFMjs5vNV_g","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"→ Concepto \"hibernación celular\"","guid":"eQm5V08sQ9qYk0e3LlWpoQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"43","text":"Inmunosupresión secundaria","guid":"FU-TnMz1Riq2JhlUe7_4tA","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"→ Fase tardía → anergia inmune","guid":"9dAUCK3ZSQmT2EdTpWBqqw","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"→ Apoptosis linfocitaria","guid":"t-i-Q2l-RGyraodxHoPTjA","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"→ Susceptibilidad a infecciones oportunistas","guid":"JGN-NWCQRLiy-W6y_jVwZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"43","text":"EN ADULTO MAYOR: Inmunosenescencia","guid":"quIR3YkIRbiUucYXE7J9oQ","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"→ ↓ Función linfocitos T","guid":"Ezv6A9DEQcmkBfbrAW1xkw","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"→ ↓ Respuesta innata (neutrófilos, NK)","guid":"ReUjyxeeSy2KkPV1C9JdIA","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"→ Inflamaging basal → respuesta inflamatoria atípica","guid":"Lr4cklw6TMarIGN6rSZoWg","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"61","text":"→ Menor reserva fisiológica → falla orgánica precoz","guid":"U23taD9JTz6ERDRk_ejHug","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"0","text":"PRESENTACIÓN CLÍNICA EN URGENCIAS","guid":"6vhTV74EStSdLGCcSkV3fA","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"Presentación clásica","guid":"Pn2yiwt3RV2NSXoHIMC8jQ","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"→ Fiebre + taquicardia + hipotensión + taquipnea","guid":"njfqrbSQSC-r3LaFijkZkg","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"→ Foco infeccioso identificable","guid":"_QS3cDVPRwW_ecnlLNdPyg","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"→ Leucocitosis con desviación izquierda","guid":"8v42DeVXTQGt4MRvYT9gaQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"66","text":"PRESENTACIÓN ATÍPICA EN ADULTO MAYOR (CRÍTICO)","guid":"z4aipX97RnmPP9Rk14pwgg","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"→ Ausencia de fiebre en 30-50% (hipotermia = mal pronóstico)","guid":"w5OzonRuT4iGHnHfDZK7-Q","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"71","text":"→ Delirium como PRIMER síntoma (50-70%)","guid":"3xJu1h4eTBG4xEyzg-Y8gQ","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"71","text":"→ Deterioro funcional agudo sin fiebre","guid":"0nzG0JCkQC2FGIeuv_GhXw","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"71","text":"→ Caída como presentación inicial","guid":"-lw_JCg4Qz2CxCRVob3G9w","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"71","text":"→ Anorexia/rechazo alimentario","guid":"UvnwFgB4SkKa4YjyAzgh1g","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"71","text":"→ Taquicardia atenuada (β-bloqueadores, deterioro cronótropo)","guid":"i14zzZzkQVuP0tssCLhZCA","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"71","text":"→ Hipotensión más precoz x menor reserva CV","guid":"HzmEX3ejT1qn2bEV8f2DCw","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"71","text":"→ Leucocitosis PUEDE estar ausente → bandas y PCR/PCT más útiles","guid":"YiTD6gXdRU2XQ5n02AaNGA","children":[]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"66","text":"Laboratorio inicial","guid":"D_PDBWE4TI2KhQrMzOzrlw","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"→ Hemograma con diferencial","guid":"WbChgGWfRKmPy9AOKZtu9g","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"→ PCR, procalcitonina (PCT)","guid":"iNeNAJLdRGqs9eOM8WuzHQ","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"→ Lactato arterial o venoso (MANDATORIO)","guid":"v-ZwL7C1SQCQT66dkffv4Q","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"80","text":"→ Función renal, electrolitos","guid":"pOzg97K1SR-vJPcPaYBp-w","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"80","text":"→ Gases arteriales","guid":"_rNV2RM4RSqaNnsJPqOo7Q","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"80","text":"→ Bilirrubina, coagulación (INR, fibrinógeno)","guid":"CsqLRNMQQTeX7j6zx58tDg","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"80","text":"→ Hemocultivos x2 (ANTES de ATB)","guid":"kyz7PX8BTtmV2EuX2UDbTA","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"80","text":"→ Urocultivo, cultivos según foco","guid":"ix7WPYx-RAOlBf3i7P6p7Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"66","text":"Imágenes según foco sospechado","guid":"PEjUhPIBRPSqrOVd14-ohw","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"→ Rx tórax (foco pulmonar)","guid":"WQmGfuMWQde5B_GFcFYavQ","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"→ TAC abdomen-pelvis (foco abdominal)","guid":"ZSSzSdF5SSesSUMmFGN7Ug","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"89","text":"→ Ecografía (colecciones, vía urinaria)","guid":"DI6QivDlQZaDkx37QxzPog","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"89","text":"→ POCUS en urgencias → VCI, contractilidad, derrame","guid":"TtX2lrFkQVWgUl1C1NXmxg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"0","text":"MANEJO EN URGENCIAS — HORA DORADA (SSC 2021)","guid":"aDPRMpRlRumoA6wZU9V6lQ","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"BUNDLE HORA 1 (MANDATORIO)","guid":"iSUyBdk8Rd-jXNad3iMBYg","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"1. Medir LACTATO → repetir si >2 mmol/L","guid":"pFmhauJ8TM66TYjKPuaXAg","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"2. HEMOCULTIVOS x2 antes de ATB","guid":"JYbsDrNdTlexd6vdeuU2Qg","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"95","text":"3. ATB empírico de AMPLIO ESPECTRO en <1 hora","guid":"NVVWXklXQviIAhopNlYGew","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"95","text":"4. Cristaloides 30 mL/kg si hipotensión o lactato >4","guid":"Bm1LyeK8QVG1fDG_shnz0Q","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"95","text":"5. Vasopresores si hipotensión persiste durante/post reanimación","guid":"QtzQr5b0Sd6EZHCt-CJMeQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"94","text":"Reanimación con fluidos","guid":"PoS2V8g8QrugNwDMOEc1vA","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"→ Cristaloides balanceados (Ringer Lactato preferido sobre SF 0.9%)","guid":"w-MuEMpsSYmnKwXANGG8CQ","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"→ Bolus 500 mL en 15-30 min → reevaluar","guid":"5RvWh6v0TOuBx8vyfXfLMQ","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"101","text":"→ Meta: PAM ≥65 mmHg","guid":"wTw4oizSRluSeEApopN2Uw","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"101","text":"→ Evitar balance hídrico excesivo → edema pulmonar","guid":"_UaHPt_qQ12VQvkyN7-e6g","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"101","text":"EN ADULTO MAYOR","guid":"1m1CtMu-RSyNok1CqKLglg","children":[{"id":"107","parent":"106","text":"→ 30 mL/kg puede ser EXCESIVO → riesgo EPA","guid":"sjmqZSEjT96xhR7ovveTGg","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"106","text":"→ Titular en bolos de 250-500 mL con reevaluación frecuente","guid":"E_udJom7QHiGdMCMGqhgdQ","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"106","text":"→ POCUS para guiar → VCI, líneas B pulmonares","guid":"XfE8fqj0QpGR9Kwuue0kPw","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"106","text":"→ IC previa → meta PAM puede ser menor o requerir vasopresores precoces","guid":"AWcppKNET5e1PplhPp_7rg","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"106","text":"→ PERLA: \"Resucitar con cabeza, no con receta\" (individualizar)","guid":"YA-DBYpISqe26_qjjMCuuA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"94","text":"Vasopresores","guid":"Qkzhi_kcSUWOAMKtVEBcmg","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"→ NOREPINEFRINA = 1ª línea (0.01-3 μg/kg/min)","guid":"AcplP5jzRC2twSyo-6O3bw","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"→ VASOPRESINA = 2ª línea (0.03 UI/min fija) si NE >0.25 μg/kg/min","guid":"VlFIn7WmQKqvQbTlUfJJXQ","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"→ Epinefrina si disfunción miocárdica asociada","guid":"t3V5u_MlSkaQWxjs6o8jmA","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"112","text":"→ EVITAR dopamina (mayor arritmogenicidad, especialmente en AM)","guid":"0FLhwQ0DR0KU1zUmDDeFng","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"112","text":"→ Acceso: CVC ideal, pero NO retrasar por acceso periférico transitorio","guid":"unmDCzX6QMqnLSWOndjAVw","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"112","text":"EN ADULTO MAYOR","guid":"ttbc-05xTKu-M690gkngZg","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"→ Mayor sensibilidad a vasopresores → iniciar dosis bajas","guid":"Mb1a2nMgR0W_4NwC9fA7Uw","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"→ Vasopresina precoz puede preservar perfusión esplácnica","guid":"otgC32jVSPqPTMugC3YtKQ","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"118","text":"→ Monitorizar arritmias (FA de novo frecuente)","guid":"zX38xRNMT22s-FoK2U9Y_w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"94","text":"Antibioterapia empírica","guid":"_lIziv_IQgKmx1X8tGqWSg","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"→ <1 HORA desde reconocimiento (cada hora de retraso ↑mortalidad 7.6%)","guid":"V1Vq_EcTSDu764rFiZuDew","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"122","text":"→ Espectro según foco sospechado y flora local","guid":"9MzPg3j9T3WAN346i2e2wA","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"122","text":"ESQUEMAS FRECUENTES (CHILE)","guid":"iGeHo7NrQgqls5MLkfK7fg","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"Foco pulmonar → Ceftriaxona + Azitromicina (o Levofloxacino)","guid":"YlQrGdufROi94f0XYMYPAQ","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"Foco urinario → Ceftriaxona (o Ertapenem si BLEE sospechado)","guid":"kL0DIbruSvWfulwEcd0gAA","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"Foco abdominal → Piperacilina/Tazobactam (o Ertapenem + Metronidazol)","guid":"86NzS-ISSM6RB_9YLnqgDA","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"125","text":"Piel/partes blandas → Cloxacilina + Ceftriaxona (o Vancomicina si SAMR)","guid":"aHdDgDJ4T2C5YL6Bs_dM1Q","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"125","text":"Sin foco → Piperacilina/Tazobactam (o Meropenem si FDR MDR)","guid":"ABdzfwoHQ9eCnAGwG-XHtA","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"122","text":"EN ADULTO MAYOR","guid":"w-Ff1wMhQ4WMd3TgSMzk-A","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"→ AJUSTAR POR FUNCIÓN RENAL (Cockcroft-Gault o CKD-EPI)","guid":"Qn4oNeycQ4qnFiPYDMeuAw","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"→ Mayor riesgo Clostridioides difficile → considerar en elección","guid":"X_3JPkw3RmW5gYp33ClMMw","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"131","text":"→ Colonización MDR frecuente (institucionalizados)","guid":"bWECwCrlSW-X8c8lV1RLWQ","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"131","text":"→ Desescalar precozmente según cultivos (antimicrobial stewardship)","guid":"52DcePGKRg-idRz5Zqtciw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"136","parent":"0","text":"MONITORIZACIÓN Y METAS","guid":"d8mMKcYgRKuhRTmAN9DbEQ","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"Metas de resucitación","guid":"GmJnIGhRTLmXlnvq3akKyw","children":[{"id":"138","parent":"137","text":"→ PAM ≥65 mmHg","guid":"Z9U1rNbnQd-YQM953Go2rA","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"137","text":"→ Diuresis ≥0.5 mL/kg/h","guid":"R858POTTTXGr26YiVxsd6g","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"137","text":"→ Normalización/↓ lactato (clearance >10-20%/2h)","guid":"wn_NDl_6RHafGqxG7RB-Kw","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"137","text":"→ Llenado capilar <3 seg (ANDROMEDA-SHOCK, 2019)","guid":"QKLt1E3fTWGYz67E9gldGA","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"137","text":"→ SvcO2 >65% (si CVC disponible)","guid":"ylDJpHl5TxuPDSBfLdJZKQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"136","text":"Reevaluación seriada","guid":"_ryUrThFQYC81V4RDKqb8A","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"→ Cada 30-60 min en primeras 6 horas","guid":"Xv3_BHM0Qo2id2XD0gV9eQ","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"→ Examen físico dirigido (perfusión, conciencia)","guid":"m-qbJG8SR7mP1HuqDj7eZg","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"143","text":"→ Respuesta a fluidos → test de elevación pasiva de piernas","guid":"qxOcQRZ5Qd2Uj4HtHltnNg","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"143","text":"→ Lactato seriado cada 2-4 horas","guid":"HIUax-G0Qei_Oo0gfrPNFw","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"136","text":"POCUS en sepsis (protocolo RUSH)","guid":"QYpOm8nrSJSYV7-KEMVtCQ","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"→ Bomba: contractilidad LV, dilatación VD","guid":"2f7PibUuTTiQyMQEqX5LGg","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"→ Tanque: VCI (colapsabilidad), derrame pleural/pericárdico","guid":"6-JY28y2TOe-3ccCYH4LsQ","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"148","text":"→ Tubería: aorta, TVP","guid":"N1CC23xWQ9m_h5ecRW_lFQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"0","text":"CONSIDERACIONES GERIÁTRICAS ESPECÍFICAS","guid":"eRcIFLFmR96JzlBP54tWHg","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"Evaluación de fragilidad en urgencias","guid":"q2cd-BCgS0qJMHhIaMek4g","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"→ CFS (Clinical Frailty Scale) → aplicar al ingreso","guid":"DLnAtjk6S1u6sxjUgbEWZw","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"153","text":"→ CFS ≥5 → mayor mortalidad en sepsis (Flaatten 2017)","guid":"QUs-azyFRqGo0IB9z3gwFw","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"153","text":"→ FRAIL scale como alternativa rápida","guid":"x6GNcQ-pQyGqe32Oz9U8tg","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"153","text":"→ Fragilidad > edad cronológica como predictor de outcome","guid":"r9OqIfLfTkGrCktGFUPJ9Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"158","parent":"152","text":"Proporcionalidad terapéutica","guid":"3bwDS_kQTLWUqvfiXQGm0w","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"→ Evaluar ANTES de escalar a UCI","guid":"26I0YbpmTqugxaX8FkXBgw","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"158","text":"→ Considerar voluntades anticipadas","guid":"sFnPoH5QS8KfT-NNzTcWtA","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"158","text":"→ CFS ≥7 + shock séptico → mortalidad >80% → discutir metas","guid":"H02EYdRvS5Oof5A-fCOfQA","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"158","text":"→ NO es \"no tratar\" → es TRATAR PROPORCIONALMENTE","guid":"EBp8q29jRduHXTUtuOYqGA","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"158","text":"→ Comfort care activo si corresponde","guid":"VsfIumDmScm01l5MheTeHw","children":[]}]},{"id":"164","parent":"152","text":"Delirium asociado a sepsis (SAE)","guid":"_Dm2Q2QsQmSQAG6Fqow5hw","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"→ Prevalencia 50-70% en AM con sepsis","guid":"oeCON-CfSlK0EDjDB3ZlYw","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"164","text":"→ Forma más frecuente: HIPOACTIVO → subdiagnosticado","guid":"yCIFN5F9RouaRT9OAPwqww","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"164","text":"→ CAM/CAM-ICU sistemático","guid":"jmnCtKzbQlul60ttvD9ivQ","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"164","text":"→ Manejo: tratar sepsis + medidas no farmacológicas","guid":"uYuaUWkJTquk83yAMrg3EA","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"164","text":"→ EVITAR benzodiazepinas (↑mortalidad, ↑delirium)","guid":"gC5utoQxTUCpq-qkfQ7xGg","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"164","text":"→ Si agitación severa: Haloperidol 0.5-1 mg o Quetiapina 12.5-25 mg","guid":"7PWElCrVSSOSPoXNa1g3Wg","children":[]}]},{"id":"171","parent":"152","text":"Farmacología alterada","guid":"6klY21HMSJSdgaKi_VegXw","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"→ ↓ Albúmina → ↑ fracción libre fármacos","guid":"os649Ty7Qo27ZYOiVC1G3g","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"171","text":"→ ↓ TFG → acumulación aminoglucósidos, vancomicina","guid":"Rr_i8YT5RC2-_L3Fxm5FIw","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"171","text":"→ ↓ Masa hepática → metabolismo fase I alterado","guid":"es6_7N0BS2GnL840VcQcbg","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"171","text":"→ ↑ Vd en sepsis → dosis de carga puede ser necesaria","guid":"bCJZ8FdPT96j7slcB-XN5Q","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"171","text":"→ PERLA: \"La primera dosis NO se ajusta, las siguientes SÍ\"","guid":"nv4-pLwETWylNDgxvHRZ4A","children":[]}]},{"id":"177","parent":"152","text":"Polifarmacia y deprescripción en crisis","guid":"wBZ_wiZ8SLypHbVEmhvZJg","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"→ Revisar fármacos crónicos al ingreso","guid":"chtxicX7TR28OenyEaeZmA","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"177","text":"→ Suspender: estatinas, AAS (si no SCA), antihipertensivos, metformina","guid":"Nyrf30VOSN-waIhWntSsmQ","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"177","text":"→ Mantener: levotiroxina, corticoides crónicos, antiepilépticos","guid":"Fm8twRN5T4GyrlJTyKIOMw","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"177","text":"→ AJUSTAR: anticoagulantes, insulina","guid":"eI1SvGEWQmOuH-Fm4I2UsA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"0","text":"COMPLICACIONES Y ESCALAMIENTO","guid":"NBxKbI8WRgeF-3Zz5YixoQ","children":[{"id":"183","parent":"182","text":"Indicaciones de UCI","guid":"p31yVKo8SDSu-tk2yCgv7g","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"→ Necesidad de vasopresores","guid":"E5fXiu03ROe7yoDDgz0zvA","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"183","text":"→ Falla respiratoria (necesidad VM)","guid":"nlGrImgNRhOY_0TPmlZFeg","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"183","text":"→ Falla multiorgánica","guid":"j-vkgkKwSuu2r05SpcG9Xw","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"183","text":"→ Lactato persistentemente elevado >4 pese a reanimación","guid":"T3dw-HthQ0KueSiz6xr2Ug","children":[]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"182","text":"Corticoides en shock séptico","guid":"GaNg4o7dQlu0f3IYYbb46w","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"→ Hidrocortisona 50 mg c/6h IV","guid":"-hiwjVIFSdGpr5e5qaVfCQ","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"188","text":"→ Indicación: shock refractario a NE >0.25 μg/kg/min por >4h","guid":"6csAzy-pTi-O87XQbevJ3A","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"188","text":"→ SSC 2021: Recomendación débil a favor","guid":"XOS6DQQkQMiDZuKEopgzSw","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"188","text":"→ Suspender tras resolución shock (no taper necesario si <7 días)","guid":"8q2xDRP6SKm1zQUZ9eT8og","children":[]}]},{"id":"193","parent":"182","text":"Transfusión","guid":"LNSKij1PQkun7XoGUQEq_Q","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"→ Meta Hb ≥7 g/dL (TRICC, TRISS)","guid":"HYhEHTByT9q5811R823e9Q","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"→ En adulto mayor con cardiopatía → considerar meta ≥8 g/dL","guid":"cx8fge2ARK2FJQzVgq1P3Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"182","text":"Profilaxis","guid":"JneaivNSRu6eJyHRg7f83g","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"→ TVP: Enoxaparina 40 mg/día SC (ajustar si ClCr <30)","guid":"6WqNYv5nQH2EdTsKg2HfJA","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"196","text":"→ Úlcera estrés: IBP solo si FDR hemorragia","guid":"cfIkq6k3S_qdOyva7nexjg","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"196","text":"→ Glicemia: Meta 140-180 mg/dL (evitar hipoglicemia)","guid":"rPV7rjH0T1GXnkrTrIMc7Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"200","parent":"0","text":"PERLAS CLÍNICAS MUE","guid":"2T3taZkXQ1KygJi8KnxfGw","children":[{"id":"201","parent":"200","text":"→ Fiebre ausente en 30-50% de AM con sepsis → NO descarta diagnóstico","guid":"aZDuHlxcS4W2eCs-xuVoVw","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"200","text":"→ Delirium puede ser la ÚNICA manifestación de sepsis en AM","guid":"enfQHci9TIqrH8gfwgdz_w","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"200","text":"→ Lactato >4 = emergencia → iniciar bundle COMPLETO sin esperar","guid":"x-E5dsW-QIOFG6ym2VBH_Q","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"200","text":"→ qSOFA tiene baja sensibilidad → NEWS ≥5 es mejor screening en AM","guid":"B-N2pp_pREC4C0wL79aP8Q","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"200","text":"→ \"Time to antibiotics\" es el predictor modificable más importante","guid":"QCSfkXU9RcOukL_H1SMQTw","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"200","text":"→ Resucitación volumétrica en AM: individualizar, NO aplicar 30 mL/kg ciegamente","guid":"d801ho3eRMC9o0DERN8c_A","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"200","text":"→ CFS al ingreso: mejor predictor de mortalidad que APACHE II en >65 años","guid":"NKNf0jphRzO44Ce3dreBIQ","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"200","text":"→ Procalcitonina <0.25 → considerar NO iniciar ATB (alto VPN para bacteriemia)","guid":"JteQcnV7TlKBHbRd1n3wWg","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"200","text":"→ ANDROMEDA-SHOCK: llenado capilar = tan útil como lactato para guiar resucitación","guid":"Fk_2aoDxQYWe3y_0gFVpAw","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"200","text":"→ Primera dosis de ATB NO se ajusta por función renal → las siguientes SÍ","guid":"RUyCTr7STZWQ7Wx9DuxVrg","children":[]}]},{"id":"211","parent":"0","text":"LR DIAGNOSTICOS","guid":"m-hkNhH1QCWXqT2Ik6DCuw","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"HALLAZGOS CLINICOS (cabecera)","guid":"IilHlvvFTNi9cnaWYtbLTw","children":[{"id":"213","parent":"212","text":"qSOFA >=2 (mortalidad hosp. con infeccion sospechada) -> LR+ 3.0 -> LR- 0.7 -> PMID:26903338","guid":"sNg7g_LaQ2q_e8Pl7WaIFg","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"212","text":"Alteracion estado mental (componente qSOFA) -> LR+ ~2.0 -> LR- ~0.8 -> PMID:26903338","guid":"4fXi9YDZTpaVAbm7YQO2Dg","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"212","text":"Hipotension PAS <100 (componente qSOFA) -> LR+ ~2.5 -> LR- ~0.8 -> PMID:26903338","guid":"AzYA5CAnQ2SterAnoXLm7Q","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"212","text":"Taquipnea FR >=22 (componente qSOFA) -> LR+ ~2.1 -> LR- ~0.8 -> PMID:26903338","guid":"Xsm3t7jeT_aC4l0PA4mgHg","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"212","text":"Hipotermia <36C (mortalidad sepsis AM) -> [LR no consolidado formalmente]","guid":"ao6n9eD3RT-IBUt50BExSg","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"212","text":"Fiebre >38C (sensibilidad baja en AM 60-80%) -> [LR no consolidado formalmente]","guid":"yf6vrftlS-e77RYY92U20A","children":[]}]},{"id":"219","parent":"211","text":"HALLAZGOS LABORATORIO","guid":"IBoWLjG0QJeDgxqXzCBIDg","children":[{"id":"220","parent":"219","text":"Lactato >4 mmol/L (mortalidad sepsis) -> LR+ 3.3 -> LR- 0.69 -> PMID:15855951","guid":"pZNeqtVvR0STdDLexdYR2w","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"219","text":"Lactato 2-4 mmol/L -> LR+ ~1.5 -> LR- ~0.8 -> PMID:15855951","guid":"LyyocDiIRYufyVxF2SJc4A","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"219","text":"Procalcitonina elevada -> [LR variable por corte, no consolidado univoco]","guid":"hHKnTxjmTZuMzaVrdzckfA","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"219","text":"SIRS >=2 criterios (sepsis en hospitalizados) -> LR+ ~1.3 -> LR- ~0.7 -> PMID:25969306","guid":"6a9LUj8FRBuF8PQgtpkV5A","children":[]}]},{"id":"224","parent":"211","text":"SCORE / REGLA CLINICA","guid":"8AvQrGVgTFi7wWKOgYX1OA","children":[{"id":"225","parent":"224","text":"NEWS >=5 (deterioro clinico) -> LR+ 3.3 -> LR- 0.25 -> PMID:23295778","guid":"KNNLGjEfRumIQVEhkfzesw","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"224","text":"MEWS >=5 -> LR+ ~2.8 -> LR- ~0.4 -> PMID:23295778","guid":"FVpkhZafTb-WWckMvmnU0g","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"224","text":"SOFA delta >=2 (definicion Sepsis-3) -> [criterio definitorio]","guid":"7KojBiCFRumNPaheFhq5LQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"228","parent":"211","text":"INTERPRETACION","guid":"MNHch-P6QeK1bW5nelttyQ","children":[{"id":"229","parent":"228","text":"LR+ >10 o LR- <0.1 -> cambio GRANDE en probabilidad","guid":"xXZyJy5_TrqfGf9sptq7eA","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"228","text":"LR+ 5-10 o LR- 0.1-0.2 -> cambio MODERADO","guid":"NAi2HDMNQ8-fqQmNF_wyTw","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"228","text":"LR+ 2-5 o LR- 0.2-0.5 -> cambio pequeno pero significativo","guid":"BPwcmd4DR7S-QA039uq4vg","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"228","text":"LR+ 1-2 o LR- 0.5-1 -> cambio minimo o nulo","guid":"GNYTT7FlTfmcZUtO-8uv0w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"233","parent":"0","text":"REFERENCIAS","guid":"VKUDBrUIRNmJunwJf8gFmQ","children":[{"id":"234","parent":"233","text":"→ Evans L et al. Surviving Sepsis Campaign 2021. Crit Care Med. 2021;49(11):e1063-e1143","guid":"Qk8hQ9L4QcW7eLGY6edD0Q","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"233","text":"→ Singer M et al. Sepsis-3 definitions. JAMA. 2016;315(8):801-810","guid":"T2N1h20_Qh6-h8UYCawt3A","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"233","text":"→ Hernández G et al. ANDROMEDA-SHOCK. JAMA. 2019;321(7):654-664","guid":"l8t2uEaTTbyHVZxFIwOWhA","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"233","text":"→ Flaatten H et al. VIP1 Study - Frailty in ICU. Intensive Care Med. 2017;43(12):1820-1828","guid":"TMljTK-OQFqorI4MZNKRkQ","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"233","text":"→ Churpek MM et al. qSOFA vs NEWS vs SIRS. Am J Respir Crit Care Med. 2017;195(7):906-911","guid":"-zGdtf8oQI69NWj82AkIQw","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"233","text":"→ van der Poll T et al. Pathogenesis of sepsis. NEJM. 2024;391:2461-2476","guid":"YDPPonA6QgWDrzIpHjN44g","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"233","text":"→ Guidet B et al. VIP2 Study - Elderly ICU outcomes. Intensive Care Med. 2020;46:57-69","guid":"jnFt54acSMGvbijZ3pmOZw","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"233","text":"→ Seymour CW et al. Time to treatment and mortality. NEJM. 2017;376(23):2235-2244","guid":"hM3o0ZbPS6eXolbLAdTnlA","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":241,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"MUE - Medicina de Urgencia","filename":"MUE_Sepsis_Shock_Septico","id":"map_2513","resolved_references":[]}